George G. Beasley



Mr. George G. Beasley is Chairman at Beasley Broadcast Group, Inc. Mr. Beasley was previously employed as a Trustee by Appalachian State University, Chairman by Appalachian State University Foundation, Inc., and President by North Carolina Association of Broadcasters. He received his undergraduate degree from Appalachian State University and a graduate degree from Appalachian State University.



